values:
I hate this plane. I really do, I don't want to be on it. I just want to...I just don't want to be on it. 

It shakes all the times, and makes me sick. I can't eat, I can't sleep. I have to much on my mind. I can barely write. I just want to see my Mollie. My beloved angel. My perfect Angel. I want to hold her. I wish she was here with me. Wouldn't that be just wonderful. 

Tyler and Mollie on another whirlwind adventure....
